				\begin{document}$${\beta }_{u,t}={\beta }_{0}{e}^{-{\alpha }_{l}{I}_{u,t}},$$\end{document}βu,t=β0e−αlIu,t,where β0 ∈ [0, 1] is the basic infection probability, αl sets the strength of the local awareness behavior, and Iu,t is the number of infectious neighbors of node u at time t. In case of global awareness, all infectious nodes u have the same infection probability at time t :2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
